lead_paragraph: Tynice Martin scored 21 points and Teana Muldrow added 19 as No. 12 West Virginia remained unbeaten with an 83-61 victory over TCU in a Big 12 Conference opener on Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: No. 12 West Virginia Women 13-0, Beat TCU 83-61
